39\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u063a\u064e\u0644\u0651\u0650\u0633\u0650 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0636\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0644 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0639\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0636 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062e\u064e\u0627\u0641\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0645\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17378,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/30\/tawbah-shaytan-wants-tired\/","url_meta":{"origin":23916,"position":2},"title":"Hasan on Tawbah: Satan wants you to tire of repentance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 30, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ja\u2019far ibn Burqan reported: I said to a man from Basra, \u201cHow can one of us continue to kneel before his Lord, seeking his forgiveness for a sin, then he returns to sin, then again he seeks forgiveness, then again he returns to sin?\u201d It was mentioned to Al-Hasan al-Basri,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32828,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/19\/fudayl-on-manhood-masculinity\/","url_meta":{"origin":23916,"position":3},"title":"Fudayl on Manhood: Character flaws dishonor religion, masculinity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 19, 2019","format":fa